MWnotes: in IUCN2019 but not in layers. Synonym Eleutherodactylus savagei also not in layers
Not in IUCN, but listed as Arachnothera affinis everetti in Catalogue of Life. A. affinis is forest dependent as well.
Bradypterus montis and B. timorensis (Dickinson et al. [2000]) have been lumped into Locustella montis following del Hoyo and Collar (2016).
Cettia flavolivacea and C. vulcania (Sibley & Monroe [1990, 1993]) have been lumped into Horornis flavolivaceus following del Hoyo and Collar (2016).
Stachyris rufifrons (Robson [2000]) and S. ambigua (Sibley & Monroe [1990, 1993]) have been lumped together into Cyanoderma rufifrons following del Hoyo and Collar (2016)
